        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 page-title">
            <h1>RENT SHARE CALCULATOR</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
            <p>
              This application is created to simplify the calculation and
              sending of the rent and utility share of each occupant of this
              flat. The monthly rent is paid on the first day of month.
              Therefore, share per person is targetted to be sent out at least a
              week prior to the rent payment, in order to collect each one's
              payment on time.
            </p>

            <p>
              Water, electric, gas (PUB bills) and internet bills are equally
              divided among the tenants. Proper division of shares is conducted
              according to the number of occupants per room for a specific
              billing period.
            </p>

            <div class="col-12 get-started">
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#steps" role="button"
                >Get started</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 home-img">
            <img src="/img/home-calc.jpg" alt="Home - Calculator" />
            <span>Figure 01. OK housemates, let's pay our rent.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
