<div id="steps" class="steps steps-bg">
  <div class="container animated fadeIn">
    <div class="content-box-inner">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12">
          <h1>HOW TO USE THE APPLICATION</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
          <h2>STEP 01</h2>
          <hr class="step-divider" />
          <i class="fas fa-database fa-5x"></i>
          <p>Register the monthly PUB cost to the database.</p>
          <p>
            Enter the <span>billing year</span>,
            <span>billing duration</span> and <span>total PUB cost</span>.
          </p>

          <a
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg steps-btn"
            href="/register"
            role="button"
            >Register PUB Cost</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
          <h2>STEP 02</h2>
          <hr class="step-divider" />
          <i class="fas fa-calculator fa-5x"></i>
          <p>
            Go to <strong>CALCULATE PAYABLES</strong> and set the billing
            period.
          </p>

          <p>
            Total rent cost per tenant can now be calculated.
          </p>

          <a
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg steps-btn"
            href="/calculate"
            role="button"
            >Calculate Shares</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
          <h2>STEP 03</h2>
          <hr class="step-divider" />
          <i class="fas fa-envelope fa-5x"></i>
          <p>
            Save the resulting calculation results, to the database and/or PDF.
          </p>
          <p>
            After securing the records, send this information to all tenants via
            email.
          </p>

          <a
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg steps-btn"
            href="#steps"
            role="button"
            >Send Through Email</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

